  "body": "**Steps:** \r\n1. Open Status app\r\n2. Go to Profile tab - Appearance - Select \"Light\" mode\r\n3. Log out and close the app\r\n4. On your device go to system settings and set Appearance to \"Dark\" mode\r\n5. Re-open the app\r\n6. Pay attention at color mode of login screen\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** login screen has dark mode (system appearance) although light mode is selected in app settings. After login app screens are displayed in light mode.  \r\n\r\n**Expected result:** Login screen should have appearance that is selected in app settings. \r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/192351000-53666aab-a5e2-4cce-bcaa-be190671c727.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
